Package: tsbox
Type: Package
Title: Class-Agnostic Time Series
Version: 0.0.14.1
Date: 2018-03-18
Authors@R: person("Christoph", "Sax", email = "christoph.sax@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools that are agnostic towards existing time series classes. 
  Converts time series from different classes and time series stored in data
  frames to each other. Functions for time series handling that work for all
  classes, or data frames, and preserve the class. Tools to make existing time
  series functions class-agnostic.
Imports:
    data.table,
    anytime
Suggests:
